units.content:
Test async stream idle timeout: use real short Duration (100ms), skip mock clock.

Pattern:
  pub const IDLE_DISCONNECT_SECS: u64 = 90;

  fn run_sse_forwarder(rx: Receiver<_>, idle_timeout: Duration, ...) { ... }

  // production
  run_sse_forwarder(rx, Duration::from_secs(IDLE_DISCONNECT_SECS), ...)

  // unit test — 100ms real sleep, no tokio::time::pause needed
  run_sse_forwarder(rx, Duration::from_millis(100), ...)

Works because 100ms is fast enough for CI, no mock clock complexity.
